THIS IS A TWO-LINE HI-RES CHARACTERGENERATOR PROGRAM. THE CURSOR STARTSINTHE UPPER-LEFT CORNER OF A 7x8MATRIX. IF YOU WANT THE DOT FILLED;PRESS 'F'; ANY OTHER KEY ADVANCESTHE CURSOR TO THENEXT POSITION. WHEN YOU REACH THEEND OF THE MATRIX; THE PROGRAM ASKSIF YOU WANT TO EDIT.WHEN YOU'RE SATISFIED WITH THECHARACTER; A 5x5 MATRIX OF YOURCHARACTER IS DISPLAYED ON THE HI-RESSCREEN. THE TEXT WINDOW DISPLAYS THE'DATA' STATEMENT REQUIRED FOR THECUSTOMCHARACTER.<PRESS ANY KEY...>TO DISPLAY THE CUSTOM CHARACTER ATPOSITION X;Y; INCLUDE IN YOURPROGRAM THE 'DATA' STATEMENTDISPLAYED BY THE TWO-LINER AND THEFOLLOWING LINES: HGR : FOR I = 1 TO 8: READ CH(I): POKE8191 + 128 * (8 * I) + Y - 9) - 984 * INT ((Y - 1) / 8) +X;CH(I): NEXT ITO USE HI-RES PAGE 2 INSTEAD;SUBSTITUTE'HGR2' FOR 'HGR' AND'16383' FOR '8191'.